        A <strong class="bg-clip-text text-transparent font-light bg-linear-to-r from-purple-500 via-purple-400 to-purple-100">new era of internet</strong> is coming.
      </h1>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<!-- -----------------End of Hero section------------------ --> 

